{{template "devtest/devtest-header"}}
<div class="page-content devtest">
	<div class="ui container">
		<h2 class="ui header">Actions build queue (drag to reorder)</h2>
		<p>
			Mock admin view of the build queue. Drag a queued row by its handle ({{svg "octicon-grabber"}}) to reorder it.
			The move POSTs <code>id</code> / <code>after</code> / <code>before</code> / <code>page</code> to a mock endpoint
			that logs them and returns 204, so the new order sticks visually (it is not persisted — reload resets the mock).
		</p>
		{{template "shared/actions/queue_list" .}}
	</div>
</div>
{{template "devtest/devtest-footer"}}
